{"tid":965929,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A/PC] 夢幻模擬戰(32)1001 11歲奶  每人一隻","createTime":"2019-01-02T11:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T02:10:01.000Z","uid":49992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d552a439a2a1f0551436d46795343ca93cb939ab","tid":965929,"uid":49992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nivsWV6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnivsWV6.png&h=53965908&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZX1scuq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZX1scuq.png&h=22d004fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Chym1nK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FChym1nK.png&h=a0dbc157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://mz.game-beans.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmz.game-beans.com&d=a%2ByH%2B75UN8%2B%2FnnxGwmERpJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=e54db652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mz.game-beans.com</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DgJzQt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DgJzQt.jpg&h=472910b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n殘體注意：陸服有傳之後會有軌跡合作角色<br />\n<a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5964106392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F5964106392&d=a%2ByH%2B75UN8%2B%2FnnxGwmERpJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=ac63a938\" target=\"_blank\">https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5964106392</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">首抽開局推介:</span><br />\n越出越多角色  每個陣營需要既核心角色都唔同<br />\n有疑問直接留言問巴打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">新手 FAQ:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 陣營有乜用?</span><br />\nA: 遊戲角色分 8 大陣營(之後會出更多)：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6V6oXca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6V6oXca.jpg&h=44917994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bs2Lq5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbs2Lq5w.jpg&h=c0cb3f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BrTiL5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBrTiL5w.jpg&h=7d907dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCq1JSc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCq1JSc.jpg&h=3f066e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EU5AOiS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEU5AOiS.jpg&h=5b95b1ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8e3Sd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8e3Sd.jpg&h=68687362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20TKGDT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20TKGDT.jpg&h=fc1f95d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BswWTiH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBswWTiH.jpg&h=4947ff87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n35級後有超絕buff要同陣營先食到(攻擊智力防+20% 魔防+30%)唔同超絕再有唔同額外效果<br />\n所以建議培養同陣營角色方便食到超絕buff<br />\n由於資源有限　<strong>強烈建議集中玩一個陣營</strong><br />\n但新手對陣營通常都會理解唔到  <br />\n目前比較多人玩係光輝帝國  光輝最平民　無課都組得起  <br />\n公主聯盟偏向法師為主   亦都比較屈機   但比較難齊角<br />\n黑暗偏向PVP  <br />\n真係唔知點揀，一係抽左角再決定<br />\n一係上黎問問巴打們<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 新手點升Rank好?</span><br />\nA: 1體=1經 組隊有折扣   前期建議組隊刷兄貴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 卡關點算?</span><br />\nA: 強化裝備 SR照突破升  拆左會退返錢同槌仔比你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 入旅團有咩用?</span><br />\nA: 以前剩係可以用黎吹水，而家多左旅團副本，打夠分會有旅團幣<br />\n可以換到魔導石(每個月一粒)同各種轉職材料<br />\n幫你慳返好多體力唔洗掃時空<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 買體可以買幾次？要用幾石？</span><br />\nA: 每日5次40--&gt;60--&gt;100--&gt;150--&gt;200<br />\n建議前期可以多買體追LV  等到後期先買少D<br />\n睇返自己經濟狀況決定<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 轉職石點用？</span><br />\nA: 每一階職第一次開係免費，所以無輪你點升都好 要精通曬2條線要2粒石，已經精通既職業可以用錢互轉，轉2階 5000錢，轉3階30000錢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 特權有冇用？買邊隻好</span><br />\nA: 廢話：最好買哂3隻  現實情況：勇氣--&gt;時鐘--&gt;女神<br />\n首先前期體力最重要  時鐘可以幫你唔夠打既時候慳體或者回帶過關<br />\n重點8蚊一個月夠哂平  但前期卡關比較容易  可以考慮30-40級後再買<br />\n勇氣(女神兄貴獎勵+1) 40級後女神會出光輝秘銀石可以升SSR裝<br />\n多一場進度就差好遠<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 點課金最抵?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\nA: 現時唔同額嘅首次增值都會有double 石<br />\nPC 版同手機版係分開計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPC版mycard增值教學:<br />\nNT$1=mycard 1點<br />\n入手方法:7-11, OK, 2000fun<br />\n1000點=HKD 265<br />\n你打開PC版，揀想課石面額<br />\n然後會彈去增值網頁<br />\n入返張單嘅卡序號同密碼<br />\n咁就完成<br />\nMycard 增值獎品會起game內信封出現<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 想退款，會唔會被 ban  account ?</span><br />\nA: 官方有講過話會打擊惡意退款, 仲整張 email 黎叫退款人入返錢俾佢，唔係告退款人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">Q: 附魔初中高級有咩分別？</span><br />\nA: 效果一樣  只係刷到好屬性既機率唔同  建議用秘銀石每星期可以換50張中級附魔卷<br />\n用中級附魔卷刷就夠   新手可以用4個初級是但附上去拎套裝加成<br />\n唔知附邊隻好  就上黎問問巴打們<br />\n<br />\n裝備評價(只供參考  升錯裝唔負責)<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=33596&amp;snA=3365&amp;tnum=10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D33596%26snA%3D3365%26tnum%3D10&d=a%2ByH%2B75UN8%2B%2FnnxGwmERpJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=2b354b89\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=33596&amp;snA=3365&amp;tnum=10</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://wiki.joyme.com/langrisser/%E5%85%A8SSR%E8%A3%85%E5%A4%87%E6%8C%87%E5%8C%97#.E5.A4.9C.E9.B9.B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwiki.joyme.com%2Flangrisser%2F%25E5%2585%25A8SSR%25E8%25A3%2585%25E5%25A4%2587%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258C%2597%23.E5.A4.9C.E9.B9.B0&d=a%2ByH%2B75UN8%2B%2FnnxGwmERpJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=2f894893\" target=\"_blank\">http://wiki.joym